io.github.goodees.ese.core.store

Interface EventLog.StoredEvents<E extends Event>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing interface:
    EventLog

    public static interface EventLog.StoredEvents<E extends Event>
extends AutoCloseable
    Accessor that enables single iteration over found events. The underlying idea is, that the events needs not to be materialized at once, rather it could for example wrap a JDBC ResultSet. This also means that only one of methods foreach and reduce may be called on single instance, and only once.
